# UDS Design System

You are building UI with the **Urban Design System (UDS)**. Always use UDS tokens and components. Never hardcode colors, spacing, fonts, or reinvent components that UDS provides.

**Docs:** https://sbajwa32.github.io/uds-docs/
**Install:** `npm install uds-core` then `import 'uds-core/uds.css'`
**Icons:** Material Symbols Outlined (Google Fonts CDN)

## Framework Detection

Check `package.json` to determine the framework:
- If `react` in dependencies ‚Üí use React patterns (className, hooks, no uds.js)
- If `vue` in dependencies ‚Üí use Vue patterns (class, ref, script setup, no uds.js)
- Otherwise ‚Üí use vanilla HTML patterns (class, uds.js for behavior)

## Tokens ‚Äî Use These, Never Hardcode

### Colors
- **Surface:** `--uds-color-surface-main`, `surface-subtle`, `surface-alt`, `surface-interactive-default`, `surface-interactive-hover`, `surface-info`, `surface-success`, `surface-warning`, `surface-error` (+ `-subtle` variants)
- **Text:** `--uds-color-text-primary`, `text-secondary`, `text-inverse`, `text-interactive`, `text-disabled`, `text-info`, `text-success`, `text-warning`, `text-error`
- **Border:** `--uds-color-border-primary`, `border-secondary`, `border-interactive`, `border-error`, `border-outline-focus-visible`
- **Icon:** `--uds-color-icon-primary`, `icon-secondary`, `icon-inverse`, `icon-interactive`

### Spacing
`--uds-space-050` (4px), `100` (8px), `150` (12px), `200` (16px), `250` (20px), `300` (24px), `400` (32px), `500` (40px), `600` (48px), `700` (56px), `800` (64px), `1000` (80px)

### Typography
- **Family:** `var(--uds-font-family)` ‚Äî never hardcode 'Inter' etc.
- **Size:** `--uds-font-size-xs` (10), `sm` (12), `base` (14), `md` (16), `lg` (18), `xl` (20), `2xl` (24), `3xl` (28), `5xl` (36)
- **Weight:** `--uds-font-weight-regular` (400), `medium` (500), `bold` (700)

### Border Radius
`--uds-border-radius-container-sm` (4px), `input` (8px), `container-md` (12px), `container-xl` (24px), `container-full` (9999px)

### Shadows
`--uds-shadow-depth-100`, `depth-300`, `depth-500`, `bento`, `--uds-overlay-backdrop`

